
## Compilation steps

1. Download latest connman tar ball from below
https://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/network/connman/

2. Go through the list of links mentioned below for understanding the support present as part of connmand
https://01.org/connman/documentation

3. To configure and generate Makefile
--> ./configure --prefix=/usr --sysconfdir=/etc --localstatedir=/var

4. Mising packages in ubuntu
  a. xtables -->  sudo apt-get install iptables-dev
  b. gnutls --> sudo apt-get install libgnutls28-dev

